OL,3,CSalford Red Devils executive quits
OL,4,Cafter alleged misogynistic language
OL,6,FSalford Red Devils chief operating
OL,7,Fofficer has resigned after alleging
OL,8,Fthat the ownership suggested she sleep
OL,9,Fwith an individual from Rugby Football
OL,10,FLeague to "smooth things over".
OL,12,FClaire Bradbury posted her resignation
OL,13,Fat the rugby league club on LinkedIn
OL,14,Fon 14 August, claiming that she faced
OL,15,Fmisogynistic and unacceptable language
OL,16,Fduring her role.
OL,18,FIn her statement, Claire Bradbury
OL,19,Fsaid: "It's important to share
OL,20,Fsomething more personal as a senior
OL,21,Fwoman in business.
