OL,3,CSalford Red Devils executive quits
OL,4,Cafter alleged misogynistic language
OL,6,F"Misogynistic, inappropriate language
OL,7,Ffrom the ownership suggesting I sleep
OL,8,Fwith an individual at the RFL to
OL,9,F'smooth things over' is not acceptable.
OL,11,F"At the time I stayed quiet because I
OL,12,Fwanted the club to succeed. I'm
OL,13,Fdisappointed in myself that I didn't
OL,14,Fstand up to it then, so I'm voicing it
OL,15,Fnow as it should be heard for the
OL,16,Fintegrity and evolution of rugby
OL,17,Fleague, and for all women who work in
OL,18,Fsport."
