OL,6,FClaire was announced as the team's
OL,7,FChief Operating Officer in October
OL,8,F2024.
OL,10,FThe club has said it "condemns any
OL,11,Fform of inappropriate language and
OL,12,Fbehaviour."
OL,14,FSalford Red Devils were bought by a
OL,15,Fconsortium in February, who said they
OL,16,Fwould clear the club's debts and put
OL,17,Fsignificant investment into the team.
