OL,6,FBut since then, the club has fallen
OL,7,Finto crisis, losing a series of key
OL,8,Fplayers and struggling to pay staff
OL,9,Fsalaries.
OL,11,FThey were also hit with a
OL,12,Fsustainability cap by the Rugby
OL,13,FFootball League in January, with the
OL,14,Fteam "directed to sell players."
OL,16,FThe club said in a statement: "It has
OL,17,Fbeen alleged by a former member of the
OL,18,FSalford Red Devils staff, who departed
OL,19,Fthe club on August 12, 2025, that she
OL,20,Fwas subjected to inappropriate verbal
OL,21,Fconduct by the owners of the club.
