OL,3,CSalford Red Devils executive quits
OL,4,Cafter alleged misogynistic language
OL,6,F"Salford Red Devils unequivocally
OL,7,Fcondemns any and all forms of
OL,8,Finappropriate language and behaviour.
OL,10,F"We treat such allegations with the
OL,11,Futmost seriousness and are committed
OL,12,Fto ensuring that our club environment
OL,13,Fremains respectful, professional, and
OL,14,Fsafe for all members of staff.
OL,16,F"In response to these allegations, we
OL,17,Fwill be conducting a thorough internal
OL,18,Finvestigation. We are determined to
OL,19,Festablish the facts and take any
OL,20,Fnecessary action to address the
OL,21,Fsituation.
