OL,6,F"We will provide a detailed report of
OL,7,Four findings as soon as the
OL,8,Finvestigation is concluded."
OL,10,FClaire went on to say: "Over recent
OL,11,Fmonths, the conditions under which I
OL,12,Fand my colleagues have been required
OL,13,Fto operate made it impossible for me
OL,14,Fto deliver my role to the standards I
OL,15,Fset for myself and for the club.
