OL,6,F"Repeated delays in salary payments,
OL,7,Fan absence of essential operational
OL,8,Ftools, and a lack of agreed structure,
OL,9,Fstrategy, or investment have
OL,10,Fsignificantly impacted the ability of
OL,11,Fstaff to perform their jobs
OL,12,Feffectively."
OL,14,FShe added the club has its "soul being
OL,15,Fripped out".
OL,17,FThe situation at the club has led to
OL,18,Fbacklash from fans. Last week, The
OL,19,FSalford Red Devils Supporters' trust
OL,20,Fchairman claimed that the club has
OL,21,Fbeen "left to rot" by its owners.
