OL,6,FA fan group, named The 1873, has also
OL,7,Fbeen set up, aimed at trying to
OL,8,Fprotect the club's future.
OL,10,FThe 1873 posted on X: "We stand with
OL,11,FClaire Butters. Her brave account of
OL,12,Fappalling conditions & misogyny under
OL,13,FSalford's owners is damning. This is
OL,14,Fthe final nail in their coffin ` they
OL,15,Fhave no place at our club."
OL,17,FIt has also posted about a protest
OL,18,Fagainst the club's owners on Sunday,
OL,19,F17 August when the team plays
OL,20,FWakefield Trinity at home.
