OL,6,FSalford Red Devils play at the council-
OL,7,Fowned Salford Community Stadium, which
OL,8,Fis also home to Sale Sharks.
OL,10,FSalford Mayor Paul Dennett said: "As
OL,11,Ffans of rugby league and the place
OL,12,Frugby has in the fabric of our city,
OL,13,Fwe share the concerns of fans. Recent
OL,14,Freports about the increasing financial
OL,15,Finstability of the club are extremely
OL,16,Fworrying. They raise concerns about
OL,17,Fthe welfare of staff and players."
OL,19,FSalford Red Devils are currently
OL,20,Fsitting bottom of the Betfred Super
OL,21,FLeague.
